{"tid":592409,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全國兩會】反白眼藐爆女行家 強國最「騷」女記者傳遭封殺","createTime":"2018-03-14T07:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T13:00:23.000Z","uid":4242,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d63d2074873ea07668bc695f23ad0429f2fa6041","tid":592409,"uid":4242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T07:44:43.000Z","msg":"一個反白眼，可以令你瞬間爆紅，又或讓你被封殺？全國人大會議日前會場外有大批記者採訪出席會議的部長，其中一名女記者，在行家提問時表現得相當不耐煩，還反了一個白眼「藐爆」對方，過程全被拍下直播出街。事後，這名女記者被傳3秒內遭「人肉搜索」，廣電總局出手吊銷她的記者證，全網封殺。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，全國人大會議日前在「部長通道」上，開放媒體訪問。其中一名穿紅衣的女記者向國資委主任肖亞慶提問時，整條問題講足45秒，但站在她身旁的一名藍衣女記者，卻從頭到尾顯得不耐煩，搔首弄姿，對着紅衣女記者翻白眼，更手托下巴，還向其他記者抱怨，甚至暗中豎起「中指」。<br />\n據悉，涉事的女記者名叫梁相宜，任職第一財經電視。至於疑似她被反白眼「藐爆」的行家，則為全美電視台台長張慧君，曾於中央電視台，並曾任職中國旅遊與經濟電視台執行台長，算是行內資深新聞工作者。事後，有傳梁相宜3秒內被「人肉搜索」，兩會新聞中心辦公室即時作出作處理，負責管理記者的廣電總局更出手，將她的記者證吊銷。有網友更指，「總局全網封殺，終身解僱。」<br />\n而今日在微博，搜索梁相宜的名字，已無法顯示相關訊息，她的個人微博亦遭封鎖。<br />\n網上更流傳有行家在微信慰問梁相宜，她說：「你翻白眼被直播了哈哈哈，太可愛了」。梁相宜則回應指「沒事滴（的）」，並直言當時之所以有如此反應，是「因為我旁邊站個傻X」、「你愁她那副德行」、「問問題比回答的（時間）還多」。<br />\n微信  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/14/154427_2921fba5b520a740606e9ca75b23e562.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F14%2F154427_2921fba5b520a740606e9ca75b23e562.jpg&h=9b3787dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180313/57940491\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180313%2F57940491&d=GCF33%2Fs%2F6JqYT7mrWSgHcaS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=971d3f1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180313%2F57940491&h=8f661d47\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180313/57940491</a>"},{"pid":"67e636ae88d8a1e18313a58989d7ddc5688c0d0d","tid":592409,"uid":50873,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T08:15:43.000Z","msg":"同邊個玩震蛋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8823b9f32b479c537b1d9ffc4388b82354e01e93","tid":592409,"uid":6352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T08:20:47.000Z","msg":"鬼國真係痴線，咁都要管"},{"pid":"b6c50205bf898f247afb47cc9b9f44806085de2d","tid":592409,"uid":60341,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T08:26:23.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，反個白眼終身唔使做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話支那好景爭住上去發展嗰啲自己睇路"},{"pid":"ce0726444e40d36e5c723a7783c06c2d7aba7e92","tid":592409,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8823b9f32b479c537b1d9ffc4388b82354e01e93","tid":592409,"uid":6352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T08:20:47.000Z","msg":"鬼國真係痴線，咁都要管"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T08:28:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾國"},{"pid":"56691ec7c232ca5de1655c0c4ce60f5c5c54c4c5","tid":592409,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T08:29:00.000Z","msg":"香港都快"},{"pid":"c0e51ee3a9c8b26804f89ec8f1213519b5bab439","tid":592409,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T08:33:52.000Z","msg":"乜係蝗國整到成個膠人咁都可以上電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31575c96a58a39d60f338c001b5edf2b6c750f95","tid":592409,"uid":160094,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T08:42:22.000Z","msg":"係就係行家<br />\n因為兩個都係高級雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126cf8a5d2766c203d399c0a1a7cf5033a7d74cd","tid":592409,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T09:38:58.000Z","msg":"個下巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4e615f8de7689b1df479881476bfcc97872353","tid":592409,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T11:29